y yield images with a flux and\npattern comparable to the Spitzer images in the bands 3.6, 4.5, and 8.0 micron.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2009 13:07:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Dec 2009 19:48:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
